data.description: Welcome Home to Griffin Park    Discover this meticulously maintained home at 211 Nobel Crest in Hinesville, GA. Boasting a spacious 2,238 sq ft floor plan, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers more than just space; it provides a lifestyle. The charm begins with a formal dining room, perfect for hosting gatherings. The kitchen, complete with a breakfast bar and overlooking the living room, creates a seamless flow for daily living and entertaining. The oversized living room is centered around a cozy gas fireplace, offering warmth and comfort. The bedrooms are generously sized, each equipped with walk-in closets for ample storage. Outside, the private backyard is a haven, completely fenced and featuring a playhouse with swing set, ideal for outdoor enjoyment. The garage boasts a bar setup, a feature the seller is willing to leave for the new owner. Additionally, the community amenities, including playgrounds and pools, enhance the overall living experience. Conveniently located near Fort Stewart and shopping, this home offers the best of both worlds - a peaceful retreat and easy access to amenities.  Secure your next PCS home now before the rush starts!
